snippet.title: Project Resistance Gameplay Overview
snippet.description:
Will you work with your allies as a Survivor, or will you crush their attempt to escape as the vicious Mastermind? The choice is yours in this 4 vs 1 asymmetrical co-op experience. #ProjectResistance

For more official news and updates, follow us on:
Twitter - https://twitter.com/RE_Games
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/residentevil/
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/re_games/ 
https://www.project-resistance.com/en/
